{
  "stem": "22892.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, finally, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, I had notice to-- if I want to go to Israel-- to the United States-- papers arrived.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I decided to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "DP camp was just like a little town-- brick buildings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Streets-- they renamed the streets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was all American names-- American states-- Ohio and, and Kentucky-- all, all American.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess-- I don't know whether they-- there were soldiers in the beginning there, American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "May have been at-- yes, American soldiers were in the beginning, when they occupied that part, you know, there were American troops.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all the streets had American names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and they had a huge-- a public bath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could go take a bath, you know, like, a couple times a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was fantastic, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember-- strange, because they have-- there was still a few Americans there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were leaving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember when I came in, and there was some-- a bar of soap in the shower.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it smelled so good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That soap, I mean, was just something I hadn't seen in years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Actually, as a kid I'd never seen-- I mean, I never had a soap that smells good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to have soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it didn't smell good at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- so I do remember about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just wonderful to take a-- to take a shower-- to stand in a shower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a child, we never, never had a shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We'd taken-- you know-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hot-water baths, but not, uh-- so that was great.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The food was, was fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, you know, it was-- you know, as a kid, I guess, there was never enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
